strategy: This matchup is pretty easy. Just respect his level 2 powerspike. Don't let him land both parts of his W or you will lose a lot of HP. Pick up an early cloth armor if you think you need it. When he Ws, you can E behind him and dodge the 2nd part; he can't proc his passive if you do this. At level 6, it's a bit harder. But the way you play it remains the same.
